{"tid":844826,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本影帝被誤當支那人怒譙「笨蛋」　網友：好大屈辱！","createTime":"2018-10-02T07:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T09:38:15.000Z","uid":32511,"like":95,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dcb162fbe5a937433fab64239fec2192f138f2ac","tid":844826,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:16:15.000Z","msg":"48歲日本演技派男星阿部貞夫在日劇、電影的演出頗受觀眾歡迎，去年更憑著和蒼井優主演<br />\n的電影《鳥獸行》成為藍絲帶影帝。昨他和吉岡里帆、千葉雄大到澀谷109百貨宣傳新片《<br />\n大聲點笨蛋！完全不知道你在唱什麼》，自爆竟被誤認是中國人的糗事。<br />\n <br />\n阿部在活動上配合片名，分享最近好想大喊「笨蛋」的不開心事情，他自爆最近曾到電器行<br />\n買東西時，竟被中國店員誤認是大陸客，對方還用普通話接待他，讓他忍不住喊：「檢查一<br />\n下笨蛋！我是日本人啊！」一番言論在網路引起日本網友討論，結果就有人留言「被誤以為<br />\n是中國人真是好大屈辱」。"},{"pid":"7caf33fd3069cb5e165d64ca6d20f91bb824ca06","tid":844826,"uid":36820,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"慘過nigga"},{"pid":"05a4ae183ba618fd7d3c56fbbf9d7df857670e8a","tid":844826,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98dea011e887f032b8aa8bacdc169c4df4d54ee","tid":844826,"uid":100766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:24:53.000Z","msg":"佢好似試過幾套日劇扮支那人/識講普通話嘅日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0097d12d8e695269939ef53c482f1aa67d7791b","tid":844826,"uid":152476,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:29:28.000Z","msg":"五毛邏輯：因為有人唔識分，所以日本人係中國人"},{"pid":"7ff1274d5f6dba374ae9e130cc05c1ebc4223c1c","tid":844826,"uid":101110,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"7caf33fd3069cb5e165d64ca6d20f91bb824ca06","tid":844826,"uid":36820,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"慘過nigga"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:40:44.000Z","msg":"做黑人俾人笑nigga都會有人走過嚟話你歧視乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n做黃種人俾人話係中國人，就好似暴風中突然吹咗塊屎片落自己塊面到噉樣。自己拼命撕走塊印住中國人三隻字臭到仆街嘅屎片外，旁人仲會避之則吉，恐防中國人屎片會沾污佢哋冰清玉潔之身。"},{"pid":"ea61efdeda468756d592b3f2816bb5164c7ce55d","tid":844826,"uid":153570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:46:13.000Z","msg":"農民工樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316c02acc18db286bee131e5262ff6bfb189e87e","tid":844826,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:48:13.000Z","msg":"留學生staff?"},{"pid":"2a549f5af67fca62734616b1adc707d86ab7cc60","tid":844826,"uid":39796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:52:27.000Z","msg":"支那人真係神憎鬼厭 過街老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b84a518d31a452ccbab7424d0ce8619f890dd8e","tid":844826,"uid":36494,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"被誤認作係支那人嗰種屈辱<br />\n好多香港人都感受過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1463347551f63bfae5e032df4206182403e6152","tid":844826,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"有無人睇左鳥獸行?"},{"pid":"ab592766b7c169e7fbc1efc176ed967db5ec4dde","tid":844826,"uid":198622,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:03:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1314e956ade48554e6015d2f25d826e91185a944","tid":844826,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd145b84c7260fa5fe4713e8adb82faf5bbec672","tid":844826,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:34:05.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為香川照之"},{"pid":"2a5473c3c147554a1176f4b413b3ba4cea453c6b","tid":844826,"uid":200328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"